text: Nizhnealkashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ismailovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 145 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Dyurtyuli, 4 km from Ismailovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Nizhnealkashevo
